data.description: Welcome to the Village at Springville! 3 bedrooms/3 bathrooms low maintenance brick and vinyl home sited on a .38+/- acre lot. Gorgeous life proof LVP in the foyer, great room, and eat in kitchen. Solid surface counter tops, pantry, tile back splash in the kitchen. Spacious master bedroom with trey ceiling. The screened back porch is the perfect spot relaxing day or night with recently built fenced in backyard. The finished basement is a must see! Springville schools, St. Clair County taxes and just minutes from shopping, restaurants and I-59. USDA 100 percent eligible!
